Package be.ac.umons.jsonschematools.generator

Contains tools to generate documents satisfying a specified JSON schema.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGenerator
    The interface for a generator producing JSON documents by using a JSONSchema.

Package be.ac.umons.jsonschematools.generator Description

Contains tools to generate documents satisfying a specified JSON schema. The produced documents have abstracted values. For instance, integer values are all represented by the special symbol \I. See AbstractConstants for all abstract values, and the non-API documentation for more information.
